README of the package esup pam_cas

pam-case is a module to a 'service' knowing UNIX authentication via PAM to use
the mechanism of SSO CAS.

pam_cas comes from the case-client distribution proposed by Yale University:
http://www.yale.edu/tp/cas/


Major amendments were made by esup-portal the initial distribution

See the documentation associated esup-portal:
http://www.esup-portail.org/display/PROJPAMCAS/Module+PAM+pour+CAS

The sources are in the source directory, and the Certificate Authority
Cybertrust root CA cert in the directory
